{"tid":108474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【慎入】【睇見都痛】唔執屋的後果 叉電器插入腳板底","createTime":"2017-02-05T09:45:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T15:36:22.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b6bf450821fb907e7cc0f45eff23b877653a6012","tid":108474,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T09:45:23.000Z","msg":"2017-02-05 16:02:00 HKT<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/05/174445_1e5fadcdcd6e4b6aa232d97bc2743004.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F05%2F174445_1e5fadcdcd6e4b6aa232d97bc2743004.jpg&h=ba02a61b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國內布拉斯加州一名少女，房間凌亂一片，難以找到「踏足」之處，結果她日前下床時，就剛好踏在隨便扔在地上的iPhone叉電器，一邊的插頭插入腳底受傷。<br />\n<br />\n18歲皮徹（Julia Pechar）的房內有不少衣服和雜物，她在床上看電視時，聽到爆谷已經煮好的聲音便跳下床。未料她踏到地上的插蘇頭，一邊插頭直插腳板，她當下痛得大叫並找媽媽求助。<br />\n<br />\n雖然受傷但她不忘自拍，「給所有嗜血的人，是的，有流血&hellip;&hellip;很多」。皮徹雖然因房間凌亂而受傷，但仍不願清理，照片在網上瘋傳，有網民坦言她的房真的是時間整理一下，笑言應有不少「隱藏物品」。<br />\n<br />\n英國《都巿報》"},{"pid":"c3a7535629cdc763a8b0c73f2e94efb519178b35","tid":108474,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T09:57:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2253e14325bbcbf280709a7a6ab4ab06343acac7","tid":108474,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T10:19:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65da9f2585436e65f6e3d55a0b943b0f7aad2c70","tid":108474,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T10:32:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f4136f7232a2db24c65e8bb1be773b9d89d2a24","tid":108474,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T10:41:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf717a040f19a1392a1c3d72687676c5dbd1aea3","tid":108474,"uid":20362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T10:49:40.000Z","msg":"我成日都驚會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e4799fddfb2326c8d73c1117a86177bdeedd546","tid":108474,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T12:22:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50d525dbc7f37ad7fffbbac24937c208bb8ca9fa","tid":108474,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T15:36:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}